{"id": "1434844864851480597", "channel_id": "1131839874132090890", "type": 19, "author_id": "920561286578856007", "author_name": "ling_an_", "author_bot": false, "content": "新的强度排行榜和朵尔加强都是在星辰篇 \n你目前的进度不需要太在意这个\n就算是打星辰篇的活动也都推荐借大佬的满配角色\n融灾的话就更不需要那么早考虑了", "timestamp": "2025-11-03T10:01:13.909000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1226164899768569956"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1434769496505319444", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1434845143793537205", "channel_id": "1131839874132090890", "type": 0, "author_id": "920561286578856007", "author_name": "ling_an_", "author_bot": false, "content": "融灾最重要的还是想办法凑出20人吧", "timestamp": "2025-11-03T10:02:20.414000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
